  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-API integration with Spotify, SoundCloud, and YouTube",
    "Server-side caching system for optimized API calls",
    "Internationalization support (Spanish/English)",
    "Dark mode with custom neon aesthetics",
    "Automated CI/CD weekly rebuilds",
    "BaseFetcher abstraction for consistent error handling",
    "Responsive UI with Astro and TailwindCSS",
